# Make Matcha — Brand Reference Guide

> This document is a comprehensive reference for Make Matcha's brand identity, positioning, audience, and visual direction. It's designed to be ingested by LLMs when making updates to the website so they have full context on what the brand is and isn't.

---

## Brand Overview

**Make Matcha** is a premium matcha company selling directly to consumers in the US and Canada. The brand sits in the top tier of matcha quality — one of only three companies importing this grade of matcha into North America. The quality delta between Make Matcha and what's typically available on the market is significant, and that's reflected in the price point.

The name "Make Matcha" is intentional: it's about handing the experience back to the customer. However you make it, make it yours. It's a creative, personal act — not a prescribed ceremony.

